Mama Cass Elliot - Don't Call Me Mama Anymore (FLAC)


Re-issue of the 1973 album from the Mama's & The Papa's diva.  Recreating selected highlights from her CBS television special. 14 tracks. 2000 release.


1. Introduction / Extraordinary - Cass Elliot, Andre, Fabian
2. I Think a Lot About You - Cass Elliot, Guryan, Margo
3. Audience Rap (1) - Cass Elliot, Elliot, Cass
4. Don't Call Me Mama Anymore - Cass Elliot, Brown, Earl [Sax]
5. My Love - Cass Elliot, McCartney, Linda
6. I'm Coming to the Best Part of My Life - Cass Elliot, Bettis, John
7. The Torch Song Medley: I Came Here to Sing a Torch Song/I Gotta Right ... - Cass Elliot, Ahlert
8. Audience Rap (2) - Cass Elliot, Elliot, Cass
9. The Night Before - Cass Elliot, Hirschhorn, Joel
10. I Like What I Like - Cass Elliot, Brown, Earl [Sax]
11. I'll Be Seeing You/Don't Call Me Mama Anymore (Reprise) - Cass Elliot, Sklar, Michael
12. Theme From L'Amour - Cass Elliot, Sklar, Michael
13. I Think a Lot About You - Cass Elliot, Guryan, Margo
14. Listen to the World - Cass Elliot, Hammond, Albert [1]
